# Dashboard Intelligence Hub — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

The main Dashboard (`/dashboard`) has been rebuilt from a simple KPI + tab layout into a **Case-Centric Intelligence Hub** with 6 analytical sections, RBAC-scoped rendering, and full interactivity.

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["DashboardHome.tsx"] --> B["DashboardSmartFilters"]
    A --> C["KPIStrip"]
    A --> D["RiskIntelligencePanel"]
    A --> E["PerformanceIntelligencePanel"]
    A --> F["FairnessMonitoringPanel"]
    A --> G["ActiveCasesTable (lazy)"]
    A --> H["ActionFeed (lazy)"]
    A --> I["RiskDrawer"]
    A --> J["CreateCaseModal"]
    K["DashboardLayout.tsx"] -->|"window event"| J
    L["dashboardDataAdapter.ts"] --> A
    M["useDashboardScope.ts"] --> A
```

