## Acceptance Test Verification Guide

| Test | How to Verify |
|------|---------------|
| **AT-Dash-01** | Run `npm run dev`, navigate to `/dashboard`. All 6 sections should render with responsive grid layout. |
| **AT-Filters-01** | Sticky filter bar visible below topbar. Change a filter → each widget shows skeleton independently. Click Reset → all filters clear. |
| **AT-Risk-01** | Click any row in the Top 10 table → Risk Drawer slides in with risk score, XAI bars, intervention text, Open Case button, timeline. |
| **AT-Case-01** | Click "Open Case" in Risk Drawer → check `localStorage` → key `smart-hr-cases-storage` should have new case → navigated to `/dashboard/cases`. |
| **AT-RBAC-01** | Log in as `super_admin` → should see only Active Cases + Action Feed, no KPIs/Risk/Performance/Fairness. |
| **AT-Perf-01** | On initial load, KPIs appear first. Scroll down — Active Cases and Action Feed lazy load (visible in Network/Performance DevTools). |
| **AT-A11y-01** | Tab through all elements → focus rings visible. Check icon buttons for `aria-label` attributes. |
| **AT-Docs-01** | File exists at [client/docs/dashboard-redesign-changelog.md](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/docs/dashboard-redesign-changelog.md) with full list of changes. ✅ |

## Key Design Decisions

1. **SVG-only charts** — no library dependency for sparklines, trends, heatmap
2. **Window event** — topbar "Quick Create Case" communicates with DashboardHome via `dashboard:create-case` custom event
3. **Mock adapter** — swap body of [dashboardDataAdapter.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/services/adapters/dashboardDataAdapter.ts) to wire real API; zero changes to components needed
4. **Dismiss persistence** — `dashboard_dismissed_feed` in localStorage ensures dismissed feed items survive refresh
